Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:01:58.88,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(498,0)}Can't focus. My body is still puzzled about what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.88,0:02:02.64,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I'm trembling. I can't stop even if I try to control myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:06.39,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Although neither sun nor moon are on my side,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:07.81,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}"I've no choice but to try,"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.81,0:02:10.48,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Those were the words I muttered to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:16.07,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(298,0)}The odds aren't on my side, but running way'd be gutless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:20.07,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(298,0)}Even if I can't see the future, I'll just have to win it over with courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:23.58,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Need to keep distance from the target as I hold myself back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:26.87,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(298,0)}All that's needed for victory is pride to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:29.96,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Will we celebrate with the wine of victory
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:33.96,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Or'll we end up kissing their feet in defeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:37.71,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}There are two outcomes to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.71,0:02:41.43,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}I want to control destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:46.77,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I need to seize the golden opportunity with my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:50.85,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I'll finish it up with my best poker face,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:55.77,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,458)}And drag them into a world of illusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:03:02.16,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I'll find my way out of this endless pressure game,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:06.16,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}And leap over the borderline of honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:10.87,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}How many? What'll I need to sacrifice to make it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:15.13,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,500)}What is the one thing I don't want to let go?
