Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.22,0:22:55.47,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,258)\i1}Let's walk together like this forever, like light and shadow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:23:00.02,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(258,0)}I stand in the city, staring off into space with lonely eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:05.36,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I can't find warmth on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:10.86,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,258)}By meeting you, I realized
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:16.70,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(258,0)}How much strength love could give me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.70,0:23:21.96,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Even if we part and meet again, I want to meet at this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.96,0:23:27.25,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Then we'll hold hands to ensure we'll never be separated again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.25,0:23:32.47,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I can't sleep by myself, 'cause I can't dream without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:38.22,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}So take me to a place where uncertainty can't reach us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.22,0:23:43.48,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}And let us bring light to the night sky with no stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.73,0:23:45.98,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\i1}So long as you're with me, I can go to world's end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.98,0:23:48.98,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\i1}Even if it's a path I can't walk on my own,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.98,0:23:52.03,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\i1}If you're by my side, I can walk it while humming a tune.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.03,0:23:55.45,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)\i1}If we're together, the world is mine.{\i0}
