Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:00:58.82,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I was a bit drunk and ended up buying a lot of flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.07,0:01:02.16,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be grateful if you'd be willing to take a few off my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:06.25,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:09.67,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.29,0:01:12.21,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:15.22,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:18.55,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:20.64,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to kindly refuse the flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.01,0:01:23.02,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I don't own a vase to put them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.56,0:01:27.98,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,But thank you for giving me a call. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:42.49,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Why does he have such good timing when it comes to things like these?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:21.47,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,A man thought to be Scar was sighted on a mountain trail near the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:23.39,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,We should start here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:25.72,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,An abandoned mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:27.14,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:30.68,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,This town, Baschool, is now a ghost town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:33.23,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,It would make a great hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:35.02,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,How troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:37.23,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,So we're going to split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:41.86,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,If a party spots him, report back immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:42.91,Default,Men,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:50.83,Default,Hein,0000,0000,0000,,We'll accompany the Elric Brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:52.12,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:54.79,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they're coming to keep an eye on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:56.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:04.05,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:07.30,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,How should we get rid of these two...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:10.93,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I just saw a shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:11.68,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:13.10,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:14.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:18.86,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:22.86,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,They disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:24.99,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Where did they go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:26.16,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Did they go into that room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:28.74,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Damn them, running around!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:36.17,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to get rid of them, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:38.17,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:40.17,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...is a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:45.09,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...too big, don't you think?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:51.06,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Scar and that little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:56.02,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If they don't randomly show up,\Nit'll be impossible for us to find them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:56.56,Default-alt,May,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Alphonse!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:59.90,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Alphonse!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:00.57,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:01.65,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:04.49,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Alphonse!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:06.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,She really showed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:09.87,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:10.99,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,May!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:13.04,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Great! I found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:17.83,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... you came here looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:20.46,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I wanted to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:25.67,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Al...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:31.39,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see you and learn more about Eastern Alchemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:35.81,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my gosh! Am I dreaming? Sir Al came looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:34.10,Default-alt,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:35.81,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:39.23,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I've been dying to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:40.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not letting you get away this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:42.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and teach us Eastern Alchemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:46.07,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,You brothers are feuding for my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:49.41,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,But you're not my type, Edward!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:50.91,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:52.62,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Al...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:54.62,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:57.50,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:59.46,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I hit my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:01.84,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that woman, Sir Alphonse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:05.46,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,How horrible... You have me, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:08.51,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,No! She's just an old friend of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:13.14,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Why am I talking like a two-timer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:16.77,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,May, please don't run off by yourself-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:19.52,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,The Elric Brothers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:21.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:24.32,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Marcoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:26.11,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Marcoh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:28.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:30.99,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:34.58,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,The Elric Brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:36.79,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:38.79,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare say you forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:42.58,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yoki, the great coal-mine owner of Youswell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:43.75,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:45.71,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I don't even think I know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:49.59,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,How awful! After all those things you did to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:56.72,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Youswell, a mining town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:07:02.06,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,I, Yoki, was a soldier and manager of the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:07.57,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,The people of the town lived happily due to my efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:28.51,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,And that's where the uttermost villain,\NEdward Elric, a State Alchemist, showed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:52.57,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,But it was a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:11.55,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,They were working together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:20.02,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,And I, who had the mine stolen from me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:24.39,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,...suffered at the hands of the people who forgot what they owed me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:27.73,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,...and was given a bad name by the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:33.61,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,I started many businesses in order to return to popularity...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:37.16,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,...but it all ended in failure...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:41.70,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,My investments...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:46.83,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,...also ended in failure...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:51.38,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,And my last resort...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:55.84,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,...was to ask a millionaire for a goodwill loan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:31.50,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,If only...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:34.05,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,If only it hadn't been for those Elric Brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:37.26,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,And that was when I swore...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:43.18,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Swore to take revenge against those two who brought me down like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:48.40,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,An act of revenge far worse than death!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:54.48,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose to a thief like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:56.57,Default-alt,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,No... I'm not really a thief...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:59.53,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, there's nothing between us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:01.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares! I need to ask you about Eastern Alchemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:03.66,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! How about you two listen to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:07.08,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, whatever. It must have been hard, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:09.37,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I totally understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:10.50,Default-alt,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Quit pretending like you were listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:15.09,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,You can't find Miss Winry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:18.01,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... what were you all doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:19.30,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're terribly sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:21.55,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:23.60,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Two men from Charlie squad come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:24.43,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:27.64,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Major Miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:30.60,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,I know. Scar, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:32.81,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,I'll contact you if I find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:46.58,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,This place is no good either, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.58,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,There's barely anything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:54.21,Default,Jerso,0000,0000,0000,,You're Scar, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:56.55,Default,Zan,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kimblee would like to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.76,Default,Zan,0000,0000,0000,,Come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:01.30,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you were able to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:06.39,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,But do you really think the two of you can take me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:10.39,Default,Zampano,0000,0000,0000,,Probably not, if we were ordinary humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:29.45,Default,Zampano,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If{\i0\fscx30} {\r} we were ordinary humans, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:31.33,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Chimeras, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:33.75,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:43.51,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I've learned a lot since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:47.26,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,First, the method to create a philosopher's stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:54.19,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Second, the history of this country. And that there's something odd about the alchemy this country uses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:59.86,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we came after this girl, seeking a possibility in Eastern Alchemy from Xing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:01.78,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing less to be expected from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:07.08,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, someone realized it far before you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:10.54,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,These are the research documents he left us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:16.29,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,We think these documents may hold a clue to solving the mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:19.67,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So if we could decipher it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:21.80,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, possibly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:26.05,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,But to do that, we need Scar's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:29.26,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Why him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:34.27,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:37.81,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,That's where Scar went!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.81,0:12:39.27,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be the army?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:42.61,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You four hide here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:44.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go see what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:48.66,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Scar is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:58.92,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,He's fat, but that doesn't slow him down at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:11.10,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you're powerless unless you can actually touch us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:14.81,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,So we're going to be attacking from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:33.29,Default,Zan,0000,0000,0000,,And we're also aware that you attempt to destroy the ground when things get bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:36.75,Default,Zan,0000,0000,0000,,We'll beat you to a pulp and hand you over to Sir Kimblee!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:43.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:46.05,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,The Elric Brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:47.59,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,This voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:52.51,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, they're Kimblee's men from Central.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:53.68,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:56.35,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:58.44,Default,Zan,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to do anything besides watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:00.73,Default,Zan,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to capture Scar-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:04.15,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,A monster!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:06.74,Default,Zan,0000,0000,0000,,W-What was that for?! We're on your sid-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:10.24,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I don't recall having any monsters on our side!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:11.32,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,How frightening!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:14.24,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to pretend they're on our side, then eat us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:18.29,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The fat one back there has a really big mouth! He'll eat me whole!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:21.25,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,You brat! Stay put!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:31.97,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Is he faster than Scar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:37.89,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:40.14,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:49.86,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So light!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:51.87,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like my limbs are made of feathers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:54.78,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Northern automails are fabulous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:57.66,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get too cocky now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:15:00.46,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I guess my punches lost some force, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:05.59,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,My spit won't come off that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:07.96,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This is slob?! That's just gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:11.51,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:17.22,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If I decompose it, it's pretty much water!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:21.52,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's cold!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:22.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:26.86,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck was that for, Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:27.48,Default-alt,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,O-O-Ow! Stop moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:28.78,Default-alt,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to tear my skin off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:33.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,How did you like my "Touching Cold Metal With Wet Hands and Getting Stuck Together" attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:37.58,Default,Zan,0000,0000,0000,,Quit getting in our way, Fullmetal Alchemist!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:39.50,Default,Zan,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you on {\i1}our{\i0\fscx30} {\r} side?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:43.12,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, pig! I don't know anyone who looks like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.12,0:15:45.25,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, anyone can tell you're a bad guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:48.88,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If you still insist that you're on our side, prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:52.01,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! I'll transform back, just watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.09,0:15:57.85,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:15:59.22,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Zampano!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:03.06,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish of you to sheath\Nyour sword in front of your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:05.86,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:07.82,Default-alt,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm going to need you to take a little nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:17.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He's in fighting shape, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:19.74,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get caught already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:22.54,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Face trial, Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:25.42,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,I'll destroy whoever gets in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:38.30,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming head-on, without thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:42.73,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Your steel arm is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:50.57,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. It's not made out of steel anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.36,0:16:57.82,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:05.08,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:20.64,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Why did you come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:25.18,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:27.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Major Miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:31.90,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's up with these two?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:37.57,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,The people at Central seem to be conducting awful experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:39.95,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Tie them to that pillar over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:41.08,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.78,0:17:43.33,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Scar...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:50.75,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't please me to pass judgment on a fellow countryman, but I can't let someone like you run free.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:52.50,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Fellow countryman?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:56.72,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Elric Brothers, we'll take care of the rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:17:59.18,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Winry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:00.76,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Stay away from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:04.39,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go... I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:06.48,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,How will you be fine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:08.39,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from him, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:10.90,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:15.36,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I want to talk to him face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:31.63,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you kill my parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:37.38,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I say, it'll be only be an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:42.39,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,The fact is I killed the Rockbells.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.94,0:18:59.11,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:00.99,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,It's in the location of the building we received a report from!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:13.50,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good. We've been down here for more than twenty-four hours, which is what we promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:17.51,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Ice Queen we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:20.55,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she really sealed the exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:22.34,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural we took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:25.26,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,We groped our way here with the lanterns out, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:29.85,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Since they insisted a monster would come if we kept the lights on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:47.99,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:49.83,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:51.83,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,Take these two to the infirmary. Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:53.29,Default,Guy4,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:54.63,Default,Guy5,0000,0000,0000,,You have nothing to apologize for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:58.88,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told you to seal the exit after twenty-four hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:02.43,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. But, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:05.22,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't been twenty-four hours yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:13.64,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Major General Armstrong told me to go by this watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:24.45,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:28.95,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Was the advance unit safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:31.41,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,Just two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:35.42,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:38.75,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, if I may ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:40.92,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking at the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:45.93,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Winter is nice here, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:47.85,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I only see black and white.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:50.39,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,It's very plain, and I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.97,0:20:52.35,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:58.36,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,If you look up, there's also the color blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:03.69,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like a person's heart, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.36,0:21:08.95,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,I greatly appreciate you giving us leeway this time, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:13.70,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:26.26,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we've got some guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:36.81,Default,Gel,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.23,0:21:44.44,Default,Gel,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for asking this the moment of my arrival,\Nbut is there something you owe us an explanation for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:21:56.66,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.66,0:21:57.54,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,All men, stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.51,0:22:07.63,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:09.43,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:22:11.26,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Kimblee!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.26,0:22:14.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell didn't you keep an eye on Winry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.27,0:22:17.98,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kimblee, the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.37,0:24:01.37,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Even if an encounter is accompanied by grief,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.87,0:24:03.96,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,there is still meaning in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.13,0:24:10.13,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The path to take is inscribed in feelings that come and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.42,0:24:15.85,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.85,0:24:19.31,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 39, Daydream.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.52,0:24:25.52,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Is everything part of a plan devised by a superior being?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:52.55,Stock,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\be25}1914
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:53.93,Stock,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\be25}Youswell
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:12.28,Stock,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\be25}Hurry up and pay
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:13.78,Stock,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\be25}your taxes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:18.91,Stock,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\be25}We can't because you keep cutting our salaries!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:32.68,Stock,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\be25}Silver pocketwatch!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:34.18,Stock,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\be25}State Alchemist!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:39.81,Stock,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\be25}Gold!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:44.06,Stock,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\be25}I want to buy the rights to the coal mine with this
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.32,0:07:58.70,Stock,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\be25}What is this about, Mr. Alchemist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:04.71,Stock,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\be25}All the gold I received from you turned into rocks!
